tanicus係傳統製法，會有好輕微煙燻味</blockquote><br />\nd速遞公司唔送液體野點算<br />\n巴打點樣買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淘寶護膚品大多唔寄香港<br />\n一定要用集運，程序好簡單，我自己用dimbuy, 比其他集運貴些少，貪佢穩定，介面方便<br />\n叫賣家寄出同埋集運申報都冩日用品就得"},{"pid":"cca921354652015f2f0efadc45caeb6858b22637","tid":282803,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:04:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩牌子好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n捷克botanicus<br />\n而家用緊佢地隻100%乳木果油<br />\n質地比較油同笠，最好晚上訓覺前搽<br />\n一盒搞掂，乳木果油功效好多，仲有學術研究支持</blockquote><br />\n講到賣廣告咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你都要講邊到買先得</blockquote><br />\n淘寶有，真貨來，一百幾十冇人會做假，記住買標題寫明有現貨的，唔係佢就會代購比你，買最細盒35g，一百蚊，一晚搽一次夠用一個月。記住只可夜晚搽，真係油膩膩的。或者日本有個品牌叫mama butter都係專做乳木果油，可以google下<br />\n<br />\n最好買傳統製法或冷製既100% grade a raw/unrefined 純乳木果油，質地好似牛油咁，因為botanicus係傳統製法，會有好輕微煙燻味</blockquote><br />\n有冇圖睇下</blockquote><br />\nGoogle search botanicus pure shea butter 35g"},{"pid":"4d41f63f65ecdcb2c5a81461686bfebf772b3800","tid":282803,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"男士如果有暗瘡問題（face or body)<br />\n可以試下去藥房買松焦油梘，三十幾蚊一舊，最多人買係英國膚適，但呢隻牌子我搵唔到佢資料，疑似實際係港牌。<br />\n<br />\n有好多人話有用，我自己經驗要用返幾曰先有小小效果。由於松焦油梘係有陣味，而且我自己用效果唔太突出，所以我都冇用。亦都可能我用來消石頭瘡（粉瘤）關係所以唔顕著，可能要用返藥膏先得，有人推介oxy暗瘡膏，我未試過，巴絲有興趣可以留意下"},{"pid":"2cb787f12114fdf090b8a6016cea6eb11be04675","tid":282803,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇乜暗倉<br />\n但想收毛孔,用咩好</blockquote><br />\n以我理解，大部分護膚品對收毛孔都冇咩明顯效果，呢方面係要搵醫生"},{"pid":"eca05c2bf3a94932be8d6d3231a2b916142a84f6","tid":282803,"uid":43849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:21:39.000Z","msg":"SK-II 認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71243d3665652ce925e042880618d240584caefd","tid":282803,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"搵醫生大家搵中環既鍾經略皮膚科醫生，佢好有料，我搵過佢兩次，收費亦好合理，所以我自願幫鍾醫生賣廣告，佢website有好多片"},{"pid":"0976256138887c585bfd5e2c17096a9136cae8b4","tid":282803,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"暗瘡點搞？<em></em>"},{"pid":"6d74f18af4d316bcac0d2242e2b3b1bcbdee6288","tid":282803,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打用過kiehls，係咪work?"},{"pid":"841dd8d309539e91248e4798a7253b8ccca83855","tid":282803,"uid":283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Lab Series</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到有得買，見好多人用</blockquote><br />\nsogo"},{"pid":"f525528bca14f67aaaff5739d2214cb0b446a915","tid":282803,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Lab Series</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊到有得買，見好多人用</blockquote><br />\nsogo</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂"},{"pid":"4a885a5051e8ebdb1a9f3697576a51aa88ecf56e","tid":282803,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20f522e53d62b4764f2db972609b8786254671f6","tid":282803,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打用過kiehls，係咪work?</blockquote><br />\n用過洗面， 磨砂， 爽膚水, 眼霜<br />\n除咗爽膚水ok之外， 其餘都嘥錢"},{"pid":"36b83c71d7d84fa7cac97873e7612d8184ceae0e","tid":282803,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:08:40.000Z","msg":"有無平既toner同保濕cream介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f093acd0d167326abd2dfa878eb516af3c2087","tid":282803,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"我用開Aesop, 啱我膚質，好用！ 不過啱我唔代表啱你，護膚品要搵隻夾你嘅牌子，唔係貴就好"},{"pid":"f65710d4fa6a400a668e9e62310b72b48215094b","tid":282803,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打用過kiehls，係咪work?</blockquote><br />\n用過洗面， 磨砂， 爽膚水, 眼霜<br />\n除咗爽膚水ok之外， 其餘都嘥錢</blockquote><br />\n得隻海底泥好<br />\n其餘唔值呢個價"},{"pid":"116de07b1f9234e7a7b2f4051cbe16afcf0ac578","tid":282803,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:17:18.000Z","msg":"上hktvmall 買啦。有得睇用家評論。無打手。"},{"pid":"fab5d55d50dd702553828f144294072e918536c6","tid":282803,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩牌子好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n捷克botanicus<br />\n而家用緊佢地隻100%乳木果油<br />\n質地比較油同笠，最好晚上訓覺前搽<br />\n一盒搞掂，乳木果油功效好多，仲有學術研究支持</blockquote><br />\n講到賣廣告咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你都要講邊到買先得</blockquote><br />\n淘寶有，真貨來，一百幾十冇人會做假，記住買標題寫明有現貨的，唔係佢就會代購比你，買最細盒35g，一百蚊，一晚搽一次夠用一個月。記住只可夜晚搽，真係油膩膩的。或者日本有個品牌叫mama butter都係專做乳木果油，可以google下<br />\n<br />\n最好買傳統製法或冷製既100% grade a raw/unrefined 純乳木果油，質地好似牛油咁，因為botanicus係傳統製法，會有好輕微煙燻味</blockquote><br />\nd速遞公司唔送液體野點算<br />\n巴打點樣買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淘寶護膚品大多唔寄<br />\n一定要用集運，程序好簡單，我自己用dimbuy, 比其他集運貴些少，貪佢穩定，介面方便<br />\n叫賣家寄出同埋集運申報都冩日用品就得</blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淘寶護膚品唔驚爆炸咩<br />\n護膚品只買日本製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10dd9e8b5df0984018d54b6d2a4d128c9bc641b","tid":282803,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打用過kiehls，係咪work?</blockquote><br />\n用過洗面， 磨砂， 爽膚水, 眼霜<br />\n除咗爽膚水ok之外， 其餘都嘥錢</blockquote><br />\n得隻海底泥好<br />\n其餘唔值呢個價</blockquote><br />\nOh no<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1831a77d15304e33189bff198bbcc08055df0c04","tid":282803,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我用開Aesop, 啱我膚質，好用！ 不過啱我唔代表啱你，護膚品要搵隻夾你嘅牌子，唔係貴就好</blockquote><br />\naesop當然正啦，又好用又好聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad2afe046919e992585e6925c5015ca8c6be36a","tid":282803,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打用過kiehls，係咪work?</blockquote><br />\n用過洗面， 磨砂， 爽膚水, 眼霜<br />\n除咗爽膚水ok之外， 其餘都嘥錢</blockquote><br />\n得隻海底泥好<br />\n其餘唔值呢個價</blockquote><br />\n泥都大把選擇， 唔需要揀佢"},{"pid":"70bc07c366c265412adeb117928b89f7aba7688a","tid":282803,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:06:25.000Z","msg":"kiehl's、aesop"},{"pid":"a138052e874c9a462fb027ec1d64b6ad7417575f","tid":282803,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T01:28:08.000Z","msg":"hktvmall 好似幾好"},{"pid":"3e2ea0db78f84895a257f3d45c2429524eea17af","tid":282803,"uid":65900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇巴打用過kiehls，係