17-06-17T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg&h=e31004e6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好用？天然野？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好用，應該唔係咩天然野</blockquote><br />\n因為有次用咗某乳液搞到皮膚敏感，出哂瘡留哂印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前白滑皮膚就咁冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家都唔知點搞好<br />\n有冇sample拎黎試？"},{"pid":"d642c2bdf87d319e4cecbbf4c7bf987ef10decab","tid":282803,"uid":12386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg&h=e31004e6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好用？天然野？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好用，應該唔係咩天然野</blockquote><br />\n因為有次用咗某乳液搞到皮膚敏感，出哂瘡留哂印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前白滑皮膚就咁冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家都唔知點搞好<br />\n有冇sample拎黎試？</blockquote><br />\n係幾好用，前日買左支爽膚水<br />\n但係有酒精"},{"pid":"c0650e9201b1fdca748fbe2808bac73e6cd3a54c","tid":282803,"uid":120567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我個post唔係要問邊隻牌子好用<br />\n係去邊到買呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓上咪答左你囉<br />\n平既去萬寧屈臣氏搵又得, 貴D既kiehl's, fancl又得<br />\n再唔係sk-ii都有男士神仙水<br />\n<br />\n是但搵個商場都有, 你行出街先得唔得姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f23d72921e979c4ddf48c5ca76eb8513404214","tid":282803,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:27:23.000Z","msg":"lm想護膚 比人話老"},{"pid":"5f83cad0c3b2848092e6417e76d1d475d35ffd59","tid":282803,"uid":72827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm想護膚 比人話老</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都老係攪就咩都唔洗攪了"},{"pid":"a3ea620d1ccf16062070ad6c3fe64c0b4cb65f35","tid":282803,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm想護膚 比人話老</blockquote><br />\n第一步<br />\n絕不買男士系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落埋哂d吸油成份，用完乾到出返油"},{"pid":"0fcd0999b78e2f1fb549b2dfd74e78cec3a792a0","tid":282803,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我用開Aesop, 啱我膚質，好用！ 不過啱我唔代表啱你，護膚品要搵隻夾你嘅牌子，唔係貴就好</blockquote><br />\naesop當然正啦，又好用又好聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係！我都鐘意個味道，唔重香料味"},{"pid":"d37b8327ab72e56f57525687540d25a8bb88abf4","tid":282803,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg&h=e31004e6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好用？天然野？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好用，應該唔係咩天然野</blockquote><br />\n要天然就用Aesop啦，佢標榜全天然原料，冇化學成份"},{"pid":"06739f83c4043960fef10e3f155cd6130eb7ff64","tid":282803,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T19:50:30.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦<br />\n治標唔治本<br />\n清完又會再生<br />\n想皮膚好，最緊要養好自己體質，均衡飲食<br />\n你諗下你每日油脂攝取量超標幾多倍？有冇食夠菜 生果？"},{"pid":"49fb5c309cbcbbc0711eeafd49f2a88645422ee1","tid":282803,"uid":72827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>lm想護膚 比人話老</blockquote><br />\n第一步<br />\n絕不買男士系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落埋哂d吸油成份，用完乾到出返油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係咩男士系列都吸油啦"},{"pid":"a049bd61527441a5238ac3773b90d178adb505bb","tid":282803,"uid":78145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg&h=e31004e6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好用？天然野？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好用，應該唔係咩天然野</blockquote><br />\n要天然就用Aesop啦，佢標榜全天然原料，冇化學成份</blockquote><br />\n買左幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1de0a2b19770ae61522280cd07414901cdcb06b","tid":282803,"uid":72827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F124548_72e0b208f9a0716fbddd387c54099311.jpg&h=e31